---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="お問い合わせ" description="Enridgeへのお問い合わせ。初回60分の無料相談を承っております。お気軽にご連絡ください。">
  <section class="bg-primary text-white py-16 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-[1080px] mx-auto text-center">
      <p class="text-sm tracking-widest text-gray-400 mb-2">CONTACT</p>
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold">お問い合わせ</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-[1080px] mx-auto">
      <p class="text-center text-text leading-relaxed mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        初回60分の無料相談を承っております。<br />経営に関するお悩み、まずはお気軽にご相談ください。
      </p>
      <form class="max-w-2xl mx-auto space-y-6">
        <div>
          <label for="name" class="block text-sm font-bold text-primary mb-2">お名前 <span class="text-red-500">*</span></label>
          <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-border rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-accent focus:border-accent outline-none" />
        </div>
        <div>
          <label for="company" class="block text-sm font-bold text-primary mb-2">会社名</label>
          <input type="text" id="company" name="company" class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-border rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-accent focus:border-accent outline-none" />
        </div>
        <div>
          <label for="email" class="block text-sm font-bold text-primary mb-2">メールアドレス <span class="text-red-500">*</span></label>
          <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-border rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-accent focus:border-accent outline-none" />
        </div>
        <div>
          <label for="phone" class="block text-sm font-bold text-primary mb-2">電話番号</label>
          <input type="tel" id="phone" name="phone" class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-border rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-accent focus:border-accent outline-none" />
        </div>
        <div>
          <label for="message" class="block text-sm font-bold text-primary mb-2">ご相談内容 <span class="text-red-500">*</span></label>
          <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="5" required class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-border rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-accent focus:border-accent outline-none"></textarea>
        </div>
        <button type="submit" class="w-full bg-accent text-white font-bold py-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-accent-hover transition-colors text-lg">
          送信する
        </button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
